- Each pod contains servie account token in the path /var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount
- bash-5.0# ls
            ca.crt     namespace  token

- Crete jwt token for each token and. each pod can receive kube-api server 
  curl --insecure https://kubernetess/api/v1/namespaces/default/pods --header = " Authorization Barier: $TOKEN" 
  
